      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. Power is delivered via a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. This vehicle has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including subframe reinforcement and Vanos service, ensuring structural and mechanical integrity. The suspension maintains its factory-tuned damping characteristics for precise turn-in, while the throttle response remains sharp. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its mileage, the powertrain and chassis are dialed-in for immediate performance use.",
